{"tid":1399660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【躺着也中槍】何韻詩在容祖兒IG留言被祖迷鬧：唔好搞我Joey唔該","createTime":"2019-08-03T08:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T11:26:45.000Z","uid":117837,"like":151,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9153987dcee265af3f192b919e06f397be8e71","tid":1399660,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190803/large/1564809083_7140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190803%2Flarge%2F1564809083_7140.jpg&h=55e2e873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左：資料圖片　右：IG截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190803/large/1564809081_4295.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190803%2Flarge%2F1564809081_4295.jpg&h=fec46909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJoey拿着空氣清新劑狂噴。（IG截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190803/large/1564809078_a6e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190803%2Flarge%2F1564809078_a6e5.jpg&h=bba1b469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿詩留言取笑她。 （IG截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190803/large/1564809076_8f87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190803%2Flarge%2F1564809076_8f87.jpg&h=3a987c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190803/large/1564809076_1829.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190803%2Flarge%2F1564809076_1829.jpg&h=66ac6cbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190803/large/1564809076_8aa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190803%2Flarge%2F1564809076_8aa6.jpg&h=ca1f90a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民留言（IG截圖）<br />\n<br />\n網民發起8月5日全城大罷工反惡法抗警暴，剛剛容祖兒（Joey）的18場的紅館演唱會於當晚開鑼，Joey近日亦忙為演唱會綵排。不過，她仍不時更新社交網站，昨晚她便上載了一段短片，拿着兩支空氣清新劑在狂噴，好友何韻詩還留言：「Chilasin」再附加一個哈哈笑公仔，未料這個簡單留言卻引來部份祖迷不滿，似乎擔心她的政治取向，對偶像有影響，有人留言說：「唔好搞我Joey唔該」、「可唔可以等容祖兒搞埋演唱會先製造混亂？求求你」，但亦有不少網民及祖兒歌迷力撐阿詩，反指那些留言的網民才在搞事，又反問為何阿詩不可以留言？甚至有人表示想見到阿詩做嘉賓。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有指不少大陸歌迷擔心近日香港局勢，成功搶購到演唱會門票都不敢來香港睇，《蘋果》的確在微博發現有不少網民以正價出售祖兒的門票，當中有人表明不敢來港，部份人則沒有說明原因，亦有人將香港近日就反惡法及抗警暴的集會或遊行時間地點放上網，提醒打算來港看演唱會的網民注意交通。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190803/59892410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190803%2F59892410&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6Jscg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=f49aad55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190803%2F59892410&h=8bc28fed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190803/59892410</a>"},{"pid":"6d6d652a1dfb2489cbfb146df15db36af44dcee2","tid":1399660,"uid":117837,"like":235,"dislike":3,"score":232,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"班祖粉痴晒線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678bafa390d5102729ec2e4fa25c41b784daee02","tid":1399660,"uid":252318,"like":145,"dislike":5,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"返去食春卷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9da4eee610fbe1ff8c5b96ff7169354fe5c8c9c","tid":1399660,"uid":117837,"like":187,"dislike":1,"score":186,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:54:09.000Z","msg":"留個言都叫製造混亂<br />\n其實好多廢老都有咁嘅思維<br />\n貼下連儂牆罷下工都叫搞亂香港"},{"pid":"ffd2a5e83b95d7d445a467ec716af4a6a0bee83a","tid":1399660,"uid":87552,"like":229,"dislike":0,"score":229,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:55:13.000Z","m